              <li>Analyze exposure, asset, and vulnerability data for elements at risk of landslides.</li>
              <li>Establish landslide damage and loss information.</li>
              <li>Establish methods and protocols for risk communication (see Hazard Response).</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
